irt]] = Players [[Redshirt (college sports)|\"redshirted']] for the 2014 season.\n\n==Schedule & results==\n''Source:'' <ref name=\"sched\"/>\n\nVisiting team on the left, home team on the right. Rankings from [[National Soccer Coaches Association of America]] (NSCAA) polls.\n\n===Exhibitions===\n{{football box collapsible\n|round= \n|date= 08/15/2014\n|time= 7:00 pm [[Central Time Zone|CDT]]\n|team1= [[Oakland Golden Grizzlies men's soccer|Oakland]]\n|score= 1\u20133\n|aet = \n|report= [http://www.siuecougars.com/sports/m-soccer/2014-15/releases/20140815gf7y8y Report]\n|team2= [[SIU Edwardsville Cougars men's soccer|SIUE]]\n|goals1= Ben {{goal|5|pen.}}  \n|goals2= Polster {{goal|24|pen.}}<br>Volesky {{goal|34|Lane}}<br>Volesky {{goal|n/a|Christianson}} \n|stadium= [[Ralph Korte Stadium]]\n|location= [[Edwardsville, Illinois]]\n|attendance= 2,346\n|referee= n/a\n|result= w\n|note = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round= \n|date= 08/22/2014\n|time= 7:00 pm [[Central Time Zone|CDT]]\n|team1= [[SIU Edwardsville Cougars men's soccer|SIUE]]\n|score= 2\u20130\n|aet = \n|report= [Report n/a]\n|team2= [[IUPUI Jaguars men's soccer|IUPUI]]\n|goals1= Garet Christianson {{goal|1st half}}<br>Danzy {{goal|2nd half|Christianson}} \n|goals2= \n|stadium= [[IU Michael A. Carroll Track & Soccer Stadium|IU Michael A. Carroll<br>Track & Soccer Stadium]]\n|location= [[Indianapolis]], [[Indiana]]\n|attendance= n/a\n|referee= n\\a\n|result= w\n|note = \n}}\n\n===Season===\n{{football box collapsible\n|round= \n|date= 08/29/2014\n|time= 7:00 pm [[Central Time Zone|CDT]]\n|team1= [[Virginia Tech Hokies men's soccer|Virginia Tech]]\n|score= 1\u20130 <sup>ot</sup>\n|aet = \n|report= [http://www.hokiesports.com/msoccer/recaps/20140829aaa.html Report]<br>[http://www.siue.edu/tv/ Live video]\n|team2= [[SIU Edwardsville Cougars men's soccer|SIUE]] \n|goals1= Grub {{yel|36}}<br>Kirch {{yel|43}}<br>Vorv {{golden goal|97}}\n|goals2= Kendall-Moulin {{yel|94}}\n|stadium= [[Ralph Korte Stadium]]\n|lo