ers#Men's soccer|Eastern Illinois]]\n|goals1= Lane {{goal|23|Volesky}}<br>Bauman {{yel|39}}<br>Lane {{goal|50|Bilyeu}}<br>Houguet {{goal|69|Meredith}}<br>Bauman {{golden goal|101|Scheipeter}} \n|goals2= Brillhart {{goal|16|Recca & Butler}}<br>Bartuch {{yel|39}}<br>Oliver {{goal|40|Brillhart}}<br>Krogmann {{goal|85|Butler & Medawattage}}<br>Butler {{yel|89}}\n|stadium= Lakeside Soccer Field\n|location= [[Charleston, Illinois]]\n|attendance= 69\n|referee= Art Arustamyan\n|result= w\n|note = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round= \n|date= 11/08/2014\n|time= 7:00 pm [[Central Time Zone|CDT]]\n|team1= [[SIU Edwardsville Cougars men's soccer|SIUE]]\n|score= 0\u20131\n|aet = \n|report= [http://www.loyolaramblers.com/sports/m-soccer/recaps/110814aaa.html Report]<br>[http://www.loyolaramblers.com/collegesportslive/?media=462237 Live video]\n|team2= [[Loyola Ramblers men's soccer|Loyola *]]\n|goals1= Hoguet {{yel|53}}\n|goals2= Bement {{goal|33|Kraussel}}<br>Thomson {{yel|41}}<br>Bement {{yel|73}}\n|stadium= Loyola Soccer Park\n|location= [[Chicago]], [[Illinois]]\n|attendance= 368\n|referee= Karl Braun\n|result= l\n|note = \n}}\n* * = Missouri Valley Conference opponent.\n\n===Post-season===\n'''[[Missouri Valley Conference men's soccer tournament|2014 Missouri Valley Conference Men's Soccer Tournament]]'''\n{{football box collapsible\n|round= Quarterfinal\n|date= 11/12/2014\n|time= 4:30 PM\n|team1=  Bye\n|score= \n|aet = \n|report=[http://www.valley-live.tv/ Live video]\n|team2= \n|goals1= \n|goals2= \n|stadium= [[Shea Stadium (Peoria, Illinois)|Shea Stadium]]\n|location= [[Peoria, Illinois]]\n|attendance= \n|referee= \n|result= \n|note = \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|round= Semifinals\n|date= 11/14/2014\n|time= 6:00 PM\n|team1= <sub>(#6 seed)</sub> Bradley\n|score= 1\u20132 \n|aet = \n|report= [http://www.mvc-sports.com/msoccer/news/2014-15/7663/msoc-championship-siue-2-bradley-1/#.VGbECvnF-So Report]<br> [http://espn.go.com/watchespn/index/_/id/2099564/2014-MVC-Me